Capital Markets

Company Overview of Guild Investment Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Guild Investment Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, domestic and foreign investment companies, and other investment advisers. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It also launches and manages hedge funds. The firm invests in public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It also invests in mutual funds, exchange traded funds, index shares, commodities, currencies, and derivatives. For its equity portfolios, the firm invests in value...
Guild Investment Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, domestic and foreign investment companies, and other investment advisers. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It also launches and manages hedge funds. The firm invests in public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It also invests in mutual funds, exchange traded funds, index shares, commodities, currencies, and derivatives. For its equity portfolios, the firm invests in value stocks of companies. It employs fundamental analysis with a focus on bottom-up research to make its investments. Guild Investment Management, Inc. was founded in 1971 and is based in Los Angeles, California.
Detailed Description


